name: Stained glass Gemini unveils
description:
Watch the zodiac sign being revealed.   

Stained glass has always been a sign of happiness as it brings colorful light to dark places. It is playful, and just for that mixing it with a puzzle-like game makes it even more lively.   

With The Twins as its symbol, Gemini is the third zodiac sign among the twelve zodiac signs. People born from 21th May to 21th June are considered Gemini natives. The element of Gemini is 'Air'. Every zodiac has its qualities based on its element. Gemini is considered Hot and Wet as it has Air element. The zodiac quality of Gemini is considered 'Mutable'. Being a Mutable sign, Gemini natives are adaptable and resourceful in their life.
